 2024-07202024-06-17GAC
ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Arrangement between the Government of Canada and the European European Union concerning the Participation by the Government of Canada in in Union programmes
PrecisOrder authorizing (1) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE EUROPEAN UNION CONCERNING THE PARTICIPATION BY THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA IN UNION PROGRAMMES; or (2) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order, to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the Agreement.
